      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/85/14",
      "text": [
        ": \"مَنْ حَجَّ عَنْ إِنْسَانٍ ٱشْتَرَكَا حَتَّى إِذَا قَضَى طَوَافَ الْفَرِيضَةِ ٱنْقَطَعَتِ ٱلشَّرِكَةُ، فَمَا كَانَ بَعْدَ ذَلِكَ مِنْ عَمَلٍ كَانَ لِذَلِكَ ٱلْحَاجِّ.\""
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2877 - Aban ibn Uthman narrated from Yahya al-Azraq, from Abu Abdullah (as), who said:\n\"Whoever performs Hajj on behalf of another person, they share in the reward until the obligatory Tawaf is completed. After that, any act performed is for the one performing the Hajj.\""
        ]
      }
    },
